</div>\n<p>效果：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>使参数变小但不完全为 0，模型更平滑</li>\n<li>适合防止参数过大，降低模型对某些特征的过度依赖</li>\n</ul>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>强度控制</li>\n</ol>\n<p>超参数 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>λ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\lambda</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">λ</span></span></span></span></span> : 控制正则化强度</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>λ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\lambda</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">λ</span></span></span></span></span> 越大，正则化效果越强，模型越简单，但可能导致欠拟合</li>\n<li><span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>λ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\lambda</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">λ</span></span></span></span></span> 越小，正则化效果越弱，模型可能仍然过拟合</li>\n<li>通常通过交叉验证选择合适的 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>λ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\lambda</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6944em;\"></span><span cl